message: I am getting frustrated being in an edit war, while the flood waters rise. Human suffering trumps editorial standards.
I am not reporting future 'civil defence plans'. I am reporting where hundreds of people are CURRENTLY being evacuated to, in the middle of a flood.
We are responding to a natual disaster. Please stop removing important information like the EVACUATION CENTRES,
